# Documentation & generated reports — kept LOCAL, not tracked.
# Functional markdown stays tracked (NOT docs): api/prompts/*.md are
# loaded at runtime via load_prompt(), evaluation/testset_prompts/*
# drive the eval harness, and the root README.md is the system intro.
docs/
report.md
slide.md
benchmark.md
pipeline/nifi/README.md
